rows.label: tlk4560015501_msg0001
rows.name:
I received a letter from Harghal,
with some money attached.

rows.label: tlk4560015501_msg0002
rows.name:
The letter wasn't long - she just asked
me not to worry about her, because
she's doing fine.

rows.label: tlk4560015501_msg0003
rows.name:
I have no idea where she might be, but
if she's happy, that's enough for me.
